name: CV / Resume Template
description:
Create super clean and professional resume today with this reusable template. Very easy to edit.


Just press T and hover on any text layer to edit the content. You can drag, duplicate and delete the components as well.


Auto-layout | A4 | Printable | Super-clean | Reusable components


Export the pages into PDF to use.


Note:

Also attached one version for the reference to match and if the editing not goes well you can unlock that version too.


"Let me know if you need any help"
